Texaco Inc's Texaco Canada said itwill raise  postings for its Edmonton/Swann Hills crude by 24canadian cts a barrel, effective June 20.    The company said the new posting for Edmonton/Swann Hillswill be 25.60 dlrs a barrel. The price hike follows a round ofcrude oil price increases started late June 17 by Sun Co. Theother major canadian crude suppliers raised prices June 18. Reuter&#3;